description: Heart & Seoul claims ground in Gainesville, Florida with becoming the first only vegan Korean eatery. The best way to bring a taste like no other is to try a signature creation "The Kimchi Taco" this dish fully brings Korean fusion to a new level. The specially picked and prepped  organic ingredients are sure to make a refreshing and healthy meal. This is definitely a place for everyone, so come on by treat yourself with Kimchi tacos or Gangdam fries. Try Heart and Seoul for a meal you wont regret!
name: Heart & Seoul
